Why action first instead of component -> Because action is shorter, 
familiar, repeatative, that's why it's easier to remmember.

Actions: Create, Delete, Change/apply/modify, Rollout, rollback, rollout 
update, show/display/describe/explain/check/verify.

Components: 
 - Cluster, Node,
 - Pod, Container, Namespace, Deployment(Repicas, StatefulSet, DaemonSet)
 Service, Persistent Volume, Persistent Volume Claim
 - Job, CronJob, Label, Annotation, Selector
 - ConfigMap, Secret
 - Monitoring(Prometheus, grafana), Networking(CNI, Ingress)
 - Tools: kubeadm, kubeblet, kubectl, kubeapiserver
 
